(b) remove, hide, replace, or modify the ZGI logo, product name, copyright
notices, or other attribution shown in the official ZGI frontend or official
ZGI Docker images;

(c) distribute, resell, or offer ZGI or a modified version of ZGI as a
white-label or standalone product under your own brand.

To request a commercial license, contact business@zgi.ai.

